COMPILING for Linux ( Tested under Linux Mint )

if GLFW3 hasn't been yet download and install it from : http://www.glfw.org/

Andrua uses C99, enable it.
Link with (-l) :
	glfw3
	rt
	m
	X11
	pthread
	Xrandr
	Xinerama
	Xxf86vm
	Xcursor
	GL
	GLU
	dl

And add library search path (-L) :
	"${workspace_loc:/${ProjName}}"
